                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Snow that never drifts --</l>
                    <l>The transient, fragrant snow</l>
                    <l>That comes a single time a Year</l>
                    <l>Is softly driving now --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>So thorough in the Tree</l>
                    <l>At night <app type="revision"><lem>below</lem><rdg>below</rdg></app>
beneath the star</l>
                    <l>That it was Febuary's <app type="revision"><lem>Face</lem><rdg>Face</rdg></app>
<app type="revision"><lem>self</lem><rdg>self</rdg></app>
Foot</l>
                    <l>Experience would swear --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Like Winter as a Face</l>
                    <l>We stern and former knew</l>
                    <l>Repaired of all but Loneliness</l>
                    <l>By Nature's Alibi --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Were every <app type="revision"><lem>Gale</lem><rdg>Gale</rdg></app>
<app type="revision"><lem>snow</lem><rdg>snow</rdg></app>
storm so <app type="revision"><lem>fair</lem><rdg>fair</rdg></app>
<app type="revision"><lem>sweet</lem><rdg>sweet</rdg></app>
spice</l>
                    <l>The Value could not be --</l>
                    <l>We buy with contrast -- Pang is good</l>
                    <l>As near as memory --</l>
